text: T'Keyah Crystal Keymáh (born Crystal Walker; October 13, 1962) is an American actress and singer. ==Roles== She is an original cast member of the Fox sketch comedy series In Living Color (1990–1994). Keymáh is also known for her roles as Erica Lucas on the CBS sitcom Cosby (1996–2000) Tanya Baxter on the Disney Channel sitcom That's So Raven (2003–2005).
